tosdr.case: Many third parties are involved in operating the service

title: Many third parties are involved in operating the service
quoteText: Third party processors of your information include: • our website hosts and operators, IT support providers, database operators, site analytics providers and software developers. • our marketing or publicity services providers. • our editorial and production service providers;• our financial services and payment service provider. • our warehousing and delivery service providers. • our auditors, technical consultants and legal advisors. and • our fraud detection services.
